# Copy to .env and fill in. Vite exposes VITE_-prefixed vars to client code
# via import.meta.env — this one is fine to be public (Mapbox access tokens
# are meant to be used client-side; restrict it to this app's domain(s) in
# your Mapbox account's token settings rather than trying to keep it secret).

# Get one free at https://www.mapbox.com/ (Account -> Tokens). Powers the
# route planner's "enter address manually" search box
# (components/ui/AddressAutocomplete.jsx). Without it, that box shows a
# small inline notice instead of failing silently.
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=
